  "description": "Symbolized an urban man with a triangle figure, a country woman with a circle, and represented the encounter between the two by movement.<br>\n<br>\nDirector Shigenji Ogino tried to naturally color the movie via the kinema color technique. Due to being an early work, the technique isn't smooth. <b>Because of this the film has a photosensitive epileptic seizure warning as there are high frequency flashes of red and green frames for the duration of the entire film.</b><br>\n<br>\nPlease be careful while viewing.\n",
